edu.iastate.cs228.hw1

Class Living

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.iastate.cs228.hw1.Living
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Animal, Empty, Grass

    public abstract class Living
extends java.lang.Object
    Living refers to the life form occupying a square in a plain grid. It is a superclass of Empty, Grass, and Animal, the latter of which is in turn a superclass of Badger, Fox, and Rabbit. Living has two abstract methods awaiting implementation.
    Author:
    Alex Huynh
